Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.61,0:01:02.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a parasite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.53,0:01:03.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What an easy way to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.94,0:01:05.50,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.85,0:01:07.62,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,...Strong enough to keep my own anger in check.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:10.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takashi! Takashi! Takashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.24,0:01:12.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Saika's purpose is to love people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.87,0:01:14.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all love each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:16.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's okay to use all of it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:22.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I live by feeding off Saika, who loves people for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:52.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Anri.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.58,0:01:53.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up so high!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:56.48,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:01.90,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.31,0:02:11.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Heiwajima Shizuo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.05,0:02:13.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:19.20,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.76,0:02:20.78,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:22.78,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He's scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:24.62,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.14,0:02:26.50,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:40.75,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:43.39,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,...knew he was incredibly strong, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:45.93,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know he was THIS strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.68,0:03:00.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something happened, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:03.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you go see what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:07.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not doing anything anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:16.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are made of the same stuff as my scythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:19.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll stop something as weak as a blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:21.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:31.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:37.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That katana...is Saika?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:41.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, before...the one who attacked me was...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:47.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You even did that to your own parents?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:57.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you didn't teach the children\N spawned from your Saika how to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:00.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:04.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell the other Saikas to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:09.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They should stop if you, the parent, tell them to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:18.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I could also order them to stop by possessing you with my parent Saika...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:19.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:21.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've suppressed Saika!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:23.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With the power of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:26.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To have someone like you who doesn't even know how to love...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:29.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you listen to something for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:33.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what's perpetually echoing inside of me:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Saika's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:38.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Words of love...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:42.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:44.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love people very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:47.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:55.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:07.45,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:11.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:11.57,Secondary Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And that was the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:18.79,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Her dad, who ran an antique shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:21.98,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,...would blow off steam by...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:24.67,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,...beating his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:31.73,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And, little by little, she closed herself off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:40.31,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That was when...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:42.11,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,the Slasher appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:02.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:07.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love...you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:15.68,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Her mother was the Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:18.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:19.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:25.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:05.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our love should have cut into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:12.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we injure someone, our thoughts \Nshould flow into his body via fear and pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.44,0:07:13.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...but he doesn't feel fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:15.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Heiwajima Shizuo doesn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:22.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey! Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:37.47,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't misunderstand;
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:41.68,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,No one loves me because they're afraid of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:43.42,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:45.39,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:48.07,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't control this power...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:50.90,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I'm constantly afraid of failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:54.16,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I'm the biggest coward in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.35,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,But so what if I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:08:01.62,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that I'm a coward has nothing\N to do with beating the crap out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:05.78,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I can't go down...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:09.38,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,...in front of the people who love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:21.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:23.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...can you stand that voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:26.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have many deficiencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:33.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I leech off things—to make up for what I lack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:40.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the heart to love people, so I can bear this voice forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:42.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever and ever, objectively—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:53.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:56.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I'd never lose to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:09:00.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:02.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Being slashed is an outcome of love, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:06.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You let me slash you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:07.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:11.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do something terrible to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:13.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So now I won't owe you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:17.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to have my Saika possess you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:25.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do, that would mean I'd have to contradict my way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:28.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'm being fair...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:33.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm trying to protect my peaceful \Nlife by doing something terrible to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:37.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I can't help it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:40.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...because I'm a parasite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:44.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:47.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Saika gets lonely easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:52.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From our point of view, it may seem wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:54.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it truly does love people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.45,0:10:00.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please love Saika, Niekawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:06.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because—unlike me—you have the ability to love people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:17.09,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:21.05,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Just frigging stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:31.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:35.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd we get like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:38.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, no one died, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:40.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:49.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.45,0:10:53.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It finally listened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:58.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anri! Is that you, Anri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:11:02.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She came after me and tried to slash me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:04.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had her transferred so she wouldn't become a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:06.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she hasn't given—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:17.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anri, let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:21.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonohara, I helped you out, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:23.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, with the Harima thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:26.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think put you and Harima in the same class?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:27.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already paid you back for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:29.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Paid me back...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:31.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean with what you just did?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:35.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that the black biker was the Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:38.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I figured he'd attack you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:42.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got lost in that thought...I wanted to help you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:43.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:45.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not because I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:48.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to pay off my debt to you at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.57,0:11:54.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was the black biker chasing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:56.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:56.81,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:11:59.65,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...from back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:02.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:03.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:05.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:10.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You too? Are you like that, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:12.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you also...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:15.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm different from Niekawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:20.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...I loathe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:35.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a prepubescent, flat-chested girl now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:41.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, what new pocket \Neditions did Dengeki release this month?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:44.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use this car for evil, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:44.90,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:47.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:50.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have they started making new chapters of "Kino's Journey?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:52.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they'll release a "Shizu's Journey!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:53.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That Samoyed Mask would...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:59.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you knew how it'd turn out if \Nyou asked Yumasaki to take care of it...psh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:01.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Togusa, your face is red.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:02.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you have a fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:05.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:09.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're okay, Sonohara?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:10.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:12.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:15.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised when I heard the news from Masaomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:17.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:19.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And, where exactly is Masaomi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:22.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He went home earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:23.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he had something to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:26.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, what could he have to do at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:28.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's really nothing wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:30.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you talked with the police yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:33.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a lot of other people besides you got hurt—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:34.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:36.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.13,0:13:41.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling...that nothing else will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:42.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:50.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I was attacked by the Slasher a few hours before I got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:54.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, a lot of people helped me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:56.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And one of them was really cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:58.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One of them was cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:14:00.50,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this development?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:02.82,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a sunglasses-wearing bartender and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.16,0:14:05.57,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, that couldn't be Shizuo, could it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:09.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And there was another extremely cool person...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:11.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't be surprised when I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:12.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:14.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the headless rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:16.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Err, uh, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:18.32,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:24.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We talked a little bit, but he was very proactive, and I could tell he has a love of others...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:27.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't believe me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:29.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say "don't believe..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.85,0:14:31.33,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,"He" is a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:37.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I was attacked again, it \Nwas the headless rider who saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.15,0:14:39.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I think I'll be okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:41.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:43.57,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:46.53,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:53.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, but, they're in a completely \Ndifferent world from us normal people...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:55.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you probably shouldn't get too involved...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:15:01.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryugamine, what do you think real \Nabnormality is in this world of ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.16,0:15:01.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:07.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's having nothing happen. It's when nothing happens over and over, day in and day out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:10.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's having nothing change.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:12.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the real...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:18.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have a doctor I know take a look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:20.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:24.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Celty, umm...I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:25.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:28.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You only did what you thought was right, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:31.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I think you did the right thing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:37.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I do think that knocking my head off was going\N a bit too far, but I'll have to take that up with Saika.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.53,0:15:41.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't mean I sympathize with you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:46.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't think I could beat you if we fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:59.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're still not satisfied, use that power you obtained to help others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:03.49,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She had obtained a power;
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.49,0:16:07.72,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,a power that enabled her to manipulate over 100 Saikas at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:11.18,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That power weighed heavily on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:14.45,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,However, that's partly what she wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.73,0:16:20.66,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone like her who was always floating on the breeze,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:24.57,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,the pressure of holding people's fate in her hands finally made her feel firmly grounded in reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:26.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:30.54,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, she heard a voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:34.02,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It said, "I may not be able to love you, but I don't hate you."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:36.59,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Or she may have just felt that she heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:39.73,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when she called out to it, it didn't respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:42.73,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,However, that was fine with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:44.77,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She became just a little bit happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:57.10,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She had finally returned to a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:03.74,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, she couldn't tell them the truth;
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:07.67,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,the truth about Saika, or about who pulls the strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:15.93,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that she'd come to control every Saika, she was able to search through Niekawa Haruna's memory, and thus found out about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:19.33,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't know his target...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:26.10,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,...but, if it happened to be either Mikado or Masaomi...\Nif he was trying to destroy their peaceful lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:31.84,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Bathed in anxiety and resolve, she remembered his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:33.53,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And that name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:38.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Orihara Izaya certainly is an odd name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:44.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be a coincidence that I was raised this way, but I think it suits me perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:47.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you believe in coincidence, Namie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:49.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:55.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They probably think all these happenings are mere coincidences...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:59.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...even though I'm the one who lead Nasujima there during that timespan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:03.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Except, he was a complete idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:07.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He could've found out Sonohara Anri's \Naddress by just taking a look at the class list.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:13.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there are lots of things that exist if you \Nlook for them with the idea that you'll find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:16.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like ethereal swords or faeries...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:22.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what actually was an accident was when he took my money and ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.69,0:18:24.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you think you borrowed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:26.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When are you actually going to pay it back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:30.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And we want it all in cash!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:26.91,Secondary Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Once he'd fallen into debt, Nasujima blackmailed the parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:30.42,Secondary Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,...of his former stalker—Niekawa Haruna—to make some cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:39.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He came to me by word of those loan sharks called the Awakusu Association and wanted me to look into Haruna's family...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:39.93,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:48.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He took the bait hook, line, and sinker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:52.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd found out that Niekawa Haruna was Saika.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:19:00.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd use Haruna to scare him by cornering him and having \Nher say something like, "You bastard, how dare you steal my money!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:01.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:05.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The real Saika—not just some copy—appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:07.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? "What happened to Nasujima," you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:16.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Give me your money!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:26.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be the best thing in the world for me if Shizu-chan were to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:28.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:31.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything went just as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:33.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you planned?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:37.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many more police around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:41.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The mass media are up in arms, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.73,0:19:44.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something happened in Southern Ikebukuro Park as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:47.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was just a clash of wills.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:48.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't the Slasher?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.82,0:19:50.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What ended up being the cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.76,0:19:54.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even that old guy didn't seem like he knew much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:59.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't remember a thing—just like he'd been hypnotized.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:06.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like the police are bracing for a gang war.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:07.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:11.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to try dying once?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:14.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, you have mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:16.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:17.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:23.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This...is from the Dollars' leader, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:27.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:35.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So...what are you after?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:41.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this city's been broken into three factions: the Dollars, the Yellow Scarves, and the ethereal sword followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:47.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And the ethereal sword followers have spies \Nin both the Dollars and the Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:54.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I would've been fine with Niekawa Haruna leading the ethereal sword group.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:57.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sonohara Anri's pretty interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:58.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:00.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with just causing some sparks for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:05.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we leave things alone, those sparks will smolder and smoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:08.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I can't wait any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.31,0:21:13.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Yellow Scarves were formed by some middle school brat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:15.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they really that formidable?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:22.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that he was able to gather that many people,\N despite being a kid...shows that they're already a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.37,0:21:29.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not like I don't know the Yellow Scarves' shogun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.84,0:21:33.48,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...drag me back into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:33.48,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,This is definitely the Dollars' doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:35.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They do whatever they want!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:38.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything without you after all, our superior!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.93,0:21:41.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not just your superior, he's the shogun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.74,0:21:43.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.08,0:21:44.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:48.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't call myself a shogun in this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:49.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a simple commoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:51.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or, a simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:54.41,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,A simple...high schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:21:57.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I just wanted to be a simple high schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.56,0:22:00.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to obtain some peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:05.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surrounded by good friends and was leading a modestly dangerous life...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:08.43,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And you've destroyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:09.86,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.86,0:22:12.88,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely can't forgive you for laying a hand on Anri.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.88,0:22:16.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We will crush the Slasher, no matter how many of them there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.66,0:22:22.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And if the Dollars are behind this, then...we'll crush the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:25.62,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,You dragged me back into this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.62,0:22:27.11,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.89,0:22:29.24,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.75,0:24:02.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.50,0:24:04.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...even though I had no intentions of doing so...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.37,0:24:06.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.54,0:24:08.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that Saki and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.24,0:24:11.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...can settle things with that guy's past.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.02,0:24:14.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time: Life and Death are in the Hands of Fate.
